@MohanDV - It looks like some care was taken previously so that getting the max of a list of mixed elements will just work.  For example `MAX([1.0, 2d, 3]) == 3`.  

Did you consider an implementation such that this would continue to work with STATS objects?  I imagine that something like the following could be made to work; `MAX([1.0, 2d, 3, stats])`?  

What do you think?

